prompts.frontCover: Minimalist greeting card front, 2D flat illustration. Two people, Jordan and Lao Lao from the photo, are rendered as cute, simplified cartoon characters. They are playfully riding a minimalist tandem bicycle across the bottom third of the card, from left to right. Jordan is in front, pedaling with a joyful expression. Lao Lao is behind him, also pedaling, with a happy, bright smile, one hand up in the air waving. Simple, elegant motion lines trail behind the bike to convey speed and fun. The background is a clean, solid off-white. In the center of the card, in a beautiful, playful handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday, Jordan". The overall design is clean, energetic, and uses simple shapes and a limited color palette.
